# The frozen Packagist metadata blobs are no longer committed (they were
# previously tracked via Git LFS, ~56 MB total). They are fetched on
# demand from a GitHub release by `scripts/fetch-cross-check-fixtures.sh`
# and verified against `fixtures.sha256`. Keep them out of the index so a
# fetch never re-stages them.
*/packagist-index.json.zst
